{"tid":2390942,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友成日嬲我掛住訓教 唔陪佢","createTime":"2021-02-02T01:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T03:49:59.000Z","uid":274180,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"315322cf75bf7b948392d3c114ecfec5c50b83e3","tid":2390942,"uid":274180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:34:30.000Z","msg":"我同我女朋友拍左拖就1年<br />\n一開始個陣 曾經都因為訓教呢件事<br />\n搞到嘈哂交咁 （佢話我啦 我無話佢<br />\n個陣 我就係個啲標準夜貓<br />\n姐係越夜越精神 朝早先訓個隻<br />\n咁佢就話我成日訓到好晏先陪佢<br />\n例如. 佢2點幾訓 我5-6點先訓<br />\n佢7點幾起身 我就晏就1-2點先起身 <br />\n咁佢話完我 我改啦 <br />\n我盡量令到自己早啲訓 <br />\n結果呢⋯<br />\n近排我就真係早訓左 <br />\n2-3點就訓左 有陣1點幾就有睡意<br />\n不過反而佢就失眠 晚晚4點先訓<br />\n例如. 佢4點幾訓 我1點話攰想恰下<br />\n同佢講 半個/一個鐘打比我就好<br />\n結果係⋯佢唔打 我一恰就朝早9-10<br />\n佢唔打比我 但會留msg比我 比說話我聽<br />\n依加佢又話我成日咁早訓 夜晚得佢一個好悶<br />\n咁我應該點做？<br />\n（佢呢排有食 有助訓教嘅藥 都無咩用 一樣4點先訓到）<br />\n我唔想因為我訓教 搞到佢唔開心 <br />\n但有陣時就係難敵睡意<br />\n我早訓早起 佢就夜訓遲起/早起<br />\nPs<br />\n訓教 我12-3點 佢就4點幾<br />\n起身 我8-10點 佢就7點/12點"},{"pid":"1dd564ff143536abbe9eb6290c7d92e7dac3f161","tid":2390942,"uid":103962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"22df576c1d4e30f99879424d89671456761d5840","tid":2390942,"uid":161794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:37:52.000Z","msg":"失眠大曬咩<br />\n如果佢有厭食症你是咪陪佢一齊唔食野<br />\n<br />\n分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6d4c8b9cd4fcf5da4f8ed0fe4ae886cc129ccb","tid":2390942,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:38:00.000Z","msg":"玩鳩你炸傻仔"},{"pid":"2493b951e39a86b8b1fdd6bc8554bf5d89adf112","tid":2390942,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:38:14.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"6c8d4706103fbb61b41958336a8d7ab55c470d78","tid":2390942,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都有女"},{"pid":"10bd9fac17088e580079295d795b64ac428cc34f","tid":2390942,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:40:23.000Z","msg":"我夜晚可以幫你陪佢解悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b807a27398e72c7c42b6d8ea2d1be8406b99a3bf","tid":2390942,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:41:59.000Z","msg":"你算好 我以前放假成日3點訓3點起身比人屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fc2556ca80d59831ccb7661a4fb0b56fc109dc","tid":2390942,"uid":44780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做乜做貓頭鷹"},{"pid":"76d24f9a4e01380ce73f545b93aec0c742015d44","tid":2390942,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair準備分手 開心～"},{"pid":"9b459ee3535a169b7b6b4039b2a88ef604d1b261","tid":2390942,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"失眠就要人陪<br />\n自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}